    XsdDownload

    public class HttpDownload
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
    Connects via HTTP to a URL and downloads the specified file. Examples: 
      <httpdownload url="http://www.centurylink.com/index.html" file="./index.html">
    Downloads the index.html file from qwest.com and places it into the current directory.
